<li><strong>Bugs </strong>(<strong>July 10</strong> and <strong>August 13</strong>)<br>
	Investigate the insects living around the house and grounds, then build a bug hotel for the Estate’s garden.</li>
<li><strong>Building </strong>(<strong>July 17</strong> and <strong>August 20</strong>)<br>
	How did Billings Bridge get its name? Construct a bridge and test its strength.</li>
<li><strong>Butter </strong>(<strong>July 24</strong> and <strong>August 27</strong>)<br>
	Explore the Billings family’s legacy as dairy farmers and learn how to make butter.</li>
</ul>
<h4><span>Notes</span></h4>
